Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:17.87,Translation,,0,0,0,,All on my own, I hugged my knees
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:23.33,Translation,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t even see that I was still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:28.34,Translation,,0,0,0,,My wound was filthy and wouldn’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:33.74,Translation,,0,0,0,,I kept on caressing it and only hurt it more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:39.89,Translation,,0,0,0,,Dreams that glowed in gold, soft and peaceful, words witnessed by the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:44.50,Translation,,0,0,0,,Slowly mixing into all the tender feelings in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:49.90,Translation,,0,0,0,,Through the rainy days, through the sunny days, every single day I loved you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:55.32,Translation,,0,0,0,,That’s the only thing I can say will always stay the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:01:00.95,Translation,,0,0,0,,But time went on, the promise unfulfilled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:05.98,Translation,,0,0,0,,My heart protected me, weak as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:11.50,Translation,,0,0,0,,and gently pushed me on, walking on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:17.64,Translation,,0,0,0,,while wishing for tomorrow’s days to shine, with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.12,Translation,,0,0,0,,One day, one of these days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.77,Translation,,0,0,0,,I’ll be able to smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.61,Translation,,0,0,0,,One day, one of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:02.22,Translation,,0,0,0,,Please allow me the freedom to feel sadness just for now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,Translation,,0,0,0,,The end to these days is broken, but I will bring an end to them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:12.40,Translation,,0,0,0,,Through the rainy days, through the sunny days, every single day you were in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:17.78,Translation,,0,0,0,,That’s the only thing I can say will always stay the same
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:23.83,Translation,,0,0,0,,And I will go down believing the promise true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:28.71,Translation,,0,0,0,,With my fragile heart held in two cupped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:34.21,Translation,,0,0,0,,you’ll gently wipe away my overflowing tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:38.63,Translation,,0,0,0,,and for your kindness I’ll say to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:46.27,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Thank you”
